/.workflow-gate-workspace/

# Public-skill local installs under .agents/skills (SoT is skills/).
# Created by `pnpm skills:install:local` / `skills:test:local` for runtime testing.
# Do not dual-commit these mirrors. Internal-only skills in .agents/skills stay tracked.
# Dual-tracked historical mirrors (commit, weekly-report, lingui-*, …) remain tracked.
.agents/skills/agentic-review-handoff/
.agents/skills/branch-creator/
